            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Pure nuclear targets in the form of thin solid discs,",
                "carbon-0.26 g/cm**2,Si-0.35 g/cm**2,Cu-0.26 g/cm**2",
                "and Zn-0.20 g/cm**2 thicknesses,were used.",
                "The neon gas was used as target also.This targets",
                "were placed inside the 2 m streamer chamber (skm-200)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".The some theoretical models-coherent tube model,",
                "wounded nucleon model,multiple scattering model,single",
                "interaction model,Dubna internuclear cascade model.",
                "The experimental data with He-4 beam on",
                "different nuclei from other author's work were",
                "reported.See Rel-Ref."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REL-REF": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "R",
                "subentry_number": null,
                "author": "M.Kh.Anikina+",
                "reference": {
                  "code": "J,YF,27,724,1978",
                  "field": {
                    "reference_type": "J",
                    "reference": {
                      "code": "YF",
                      "number": null,
                      "volume": "27",
                      "part": null,
                      "issue": null,
                      "page": "724"
                    },
                    "date": 1978
                  }
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                ".It is earlier",
                "author's data obtained with the He-4 projectiles and",
                "reported in this work also."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".The triggering set-up consisted of a telescope",
                "of scintillation counters in front of the chamber",
                "defining the beam particles by delta-E/dx measurements",
                "of the charge of beam nuclei z(p) and a veto counter",
                " (vc-system) placed behind the chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
