          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The corrections were introduced for the",
                "following effects-",
                "1. Contamination of samples of secondary negative pions",
                "with an admixture of electrons from the",
                "gamma-conversion or from the dalitz pairs,the",
                "corrections did no exceed 1%.",
                "2. Secondary interactions within the solid targets,the",
                "uncertainties due to this effect did not exceed 1%.",
                "3. The largest corrections concerned events with low",
                "multiplicity on the average being less than 5% for all",
                "samples of events.",
                "4. Errors due to the wrong estimation of the event",
                "vertex position in the case of highly collimated",
                "low-multiplicity events, the correction value depend on",
                "the mass number of the target nuclei, being 2.5% for Cu",
                "and Zn and less than 1% for C and Si."
              ]
            }
          ],
